{
  "stem": "14867.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they remembered that during the Czar, this was clandestine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They could not say that they belonged because they would have been shot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The same thing during the Stalin years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in 1920.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father was even part of the commission that established the border.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, he was the one who met, at the station, General Pilsudski, who was a big hero-- one of the greatest heroes of Poland-- who was invited to establish the border between Russia and Poland.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And since our estate was on the border, he was very much interested to be involved in it, my father, because half of the estate really went to Russia.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if he didn't go with them, he probably would have lost most of his estate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he was the one who met this general at the railroad station, with his horses and carriage.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's how he saved some of his estate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was in 1920, that--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Jabotinsky was a little bit aloof.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was one of the greatest orators, one of the greatest speakers I've ever heard.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Begin was very friendly and very, very bright.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Very sharp.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Extremely popular all over Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody predicted a great future for him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I met, also, his wife.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because later on when I  went to Lvov, I looked him up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we met.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I met, also, his wife and-- but I never met his children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He had two children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he really was a very, very prominent man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And of course, we had a formal staircase in our home, so when we had dignitaries like Jabotinsky or-- or Begin, or other Polish dignitaries, we would have a guard in front of the-- of the entrance.",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
